</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/04d326b0ae464569ba667f5b56e0541a4efe6bb4" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.338ex; width:1.42ex; height:2.176ex;" alt="{\displaystyle \veebar }"></span> (<a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/유니코드" title="유니코드" id="mwLQ">유니코드</a>: U+22BB ⊻), <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt7" data-mw="{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;math&quot;,&quot;attrs&quot;:{},&quot;body&quot;:{&quot;extsrc&quot;:&quot;\\dot\\vee&quot;}}" id="mwLg"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle {\dot {\vee }}}">
